            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <div type="textpart" xml:lang="heb">
                    <p> הדה נפשׁה דמוסיס בר מרסה דמית בשׁתה<lb/>תליתה דשׁבואה בירח כסלו בעסרין
                        ושׁבעה<lb/>יומינ ביה היא שׁנת רצ שׁנין<lb/>
                  <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>לחרבן בית מקדשׁה. <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
               </p>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" xml:lang="grc">
                    <p/>
                    <ab>Μνημῖον Μουσῖ<lb/>Μάρσου, γενη<unclear>θ</unclear>έντος<lb/>ἔτους <num value="235">σλε</num>, <unclear>ἀπο</unclear>θανόν<lb break="no"/>τος
                                <expan>
                     <abbr>ἔτ</abbr>
                     <ex>ους</ex>
                  </expan>
                        <num value="253">σνγ</num>.<lb/>Ε<unclear>ὑ</unclear>μοιρίτω.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
          
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="Aramaic">
                    <p>This is the tombstone of Mousis, son of Marsha, who died in the year three of
                        the seven-year cycle, in the month of Kislev, on the twenty seventh day of
                        it, which is th eyear 290 years of the destruction of the Sanctuary.</p>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="Greek">
                    <p>Monument of Mousi(s), son of Marsos, who was born in (the) year 235 (and)
                        died in (the) year 253. May his lot be good.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p/>
            </div>
